name: Anna von Hausswolff
description: '''Anna Michaela Ebba Electra von Hausswolff''' (born 6 September 1986) is a Swedish singer, songwriter, musician, composer, and pipe organist. She is known for her [[Gothic rock|gothic]]-styled music, usually accompanied by the [[pipe organ]]. Von Hausswolff's music has received praise from [[music critics]], though it resulted in protests from Catholic fundamentalist groups.
